{
  "text": "Completed abstraction forms (and the original medical charts if needed) were reviewed by a vascular neurologist (E.L., N.N., or S. D.). The adjudication criteria were based on the 2013 American Heart Association/American Stroke Association definition of ischemic stroke, [CITATION_1] and the addition of a \"possible\" AIS category for cases where chart information was incomplete. Potential cases were adjudicated as a definite, probable, or possible AIS, no AIS, or as status unknown/insufficient information, as described below.",
  "citation_candidates": [
